The paper deals with resource allocation in wiretap channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of multiple antennas also suggests the possibility of research in the areas of networking and communication (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
